author: Journal Inquirer Staff
title: Bolton cruises to victory
text:
Bolton cruises to victory By Journal Inquirer Staff Journal Inquirer | 0 comments 
Bolton 3, Public Safety 0 
In Bolton, Laina McCarthy had 10 aces in the host Bulldogs’ non-league sweep. Game scores were 25-14, 25-11, 25-18. 
Lauren Leavitt had six assists and a kill for Bolton (6-6).
